391
00:25:30,750 --> 00:25:32,350
He practically disappeared
for two years.

392
00:25:32,750 --> 00:25:34,070
He came with me to Dalpur

393
00:25:34,070 --> 00:25:35,310
because of a photograph

394
00:25:35,310 --> 00:25:36,920
