420
00:26:50,270 --> 00:26:52,750
(Will you
still be as bossy as you are now?)

421
00:26:53,790 --> 00:26:55,510
(I'd really like to know)

422
00:26:59,000 --> 00:26:59,550
(Because my time)

423
